---
import Layout from '../../../components/layout/Layout.astro';
import ArtworkSchema from '../../../components/seo/ArtworkSchema.astro';

const lang = 'en' as const;
const title = 'Nuevas Floras Versalles';

const img1 = (await import('../../../assets/images/obras/nuevas-floras-versalles/versalles-01.jpg')).default;
const img2 = (await import('../../../assets/images/obras/nuevas-floras-versalles/versalles-02.jpg')).default;
---

<Layout
  lang={lang}
  title="Nuevas Floras Versalles — Works"
  description="Nuevas Floras Versalles (2017). Sculptural intervention on trees at the Arboretum de Chevreloup and Jardin des Tuileries (FIAC), France. Maria Elvira Escallon."
>

  <ArtworkSchema
    title="Nuevas Floras Versalles"
    year="2017"
    medium="Sculptural intervention on trees, photography"
    description="Intervention on trees at the Arboretum de Chevreloup and the Jardin des Tuileries during FIAC, Versailles/Paris, France."
    url="https://mariaelviraescallon.com/en/works/nuevas-floras-versalles/"
  />

  <article class="work-page">
    <div class="container">

      <header class="work-page__header">
        <p class="label">Works / 005b</p>
        <h1>{title}</h1>
        <p class="work-page__meta">2017 &nbsp;/&nbsp; Sculptural intervention on trees &nbsp;/&nbsp; Arboretum de Chevreloup &amp; Jardin des Tuileries, France</p>
      </header>

      <div class="work-page__gallery">
        <img src={img1.src} alt="Nuevas Floras Versalles — Intervention at the Jardin des Tuileries, FIAC 2017" loading="eager">
        <img src={img2.src} alt="Nuevas Floras Versalles — Baroque carving at the Arboretum de Chevreloup" loading="lazy">
      </div>

      <div class="work-page__body">
        <div class="work-page__text">

          <p class="curatorial">
            In 2017, Maria Elvira Escallon brought <em>Nuevas Floras</em> to France, intervening
            on trees at the Arboretum de Chevreloup and presenting the work at the Jardin des
            Tuileries during FIAC (Foire Internationale d'Art Contemporain) in Paris.
          </p>

          <p class="curatorial" style="margin-top: var(--s2);">
            This version responds to the specificities of the French landscape and history —
            a dialogue between baroque carved forms and the formal gardens of the European
            landscape tradition. Unlike the Colombian version, where the carvings dialogue
            with colonial baroque, in Versailles the work is situated at the heart of the
            tradition that originated that same ornamental repertoire — closing a cycle between
            the European source and its Latin American reinterpretation.
          </p>

          <h3 style="margin-top: var(--s4);">ORIGINAL WORK</h3>
          <ul style="margin-top: var(--s2); list-style: none;">
            <li style="padding: var(--s1) 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--paper-dark);">
              <a href="/maria-elvira-escallon/en/works/nuevas-floras/" style="color: var(--moss); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--paper-dark);">Nuevas Floras (2003) — Colombia</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <aside class="work-page__ficha">
          <h4>TECHNICAL DETAILS</h4>
          <div class="ficha">
            <strong>Nuevas Floras Versalles</strong><br>
            2017<br><br>
            Sculptural intervention on trees.<br>
            Wood carving.<br>
            Documentation: photography.<br><br>
            Variable dimensions
          </div>

          <h4 style="margin-top: var(--s3);">LOCATION</h4>
          <div class="ficha">
            Arboretum de Chevreloup, Versailles<br>
            Jardin des Tuileries, FIAC, Paris<br>
            France, 2017
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>

    </div>
  </article>

</Layout>
